item.title: By: Marcus
item.dc:creator: Marcus
item.description: Really touching Will. Was so sad to hear the news yesterday. Not that I knew him to well, but anyone that has such a positive effect on so many of my friends must be the classiest of class acts. He was someone I wanted to know better.
